content: Glaennor was a scout with the Rebel Alliance and later with New Republic Scout Service's Eighth Nebulan Scout Corps who was known to occasionally express satisfaction at her income. In 4 ABY she and her fellow scout Andur Thorsim was saved by Luke Skywalker from Oskan blood eater released by mind-witch S'ybll.
